creator: YachtLife
descriptionHtml:
YachtLife allows you to easily charter luxury & private yachts around the world. You can easily compare prices, message yacht specialists, and rent from the app.

There’s no need to call to find prices and terms and negotiate - we’ve done all that for you. We’ve hand-picked a fleet of the highest quality private & luxury yachts and the best crews to give you the best yacht charter experience imaginable.

Once you create your YachtLife profile, you’ll be able to browse our entire global yacht charter fleet. You can always ask a question or call for further information on any yacht. Reserve a luxury yacht for your desired date, duration, pickup time, and the number of guests. Our yacht charter specialists will receive your request and confirm your yacht charter.

YachtLife operates in 30+ markets worldwide with over 500 private yachts available for yacht charter. Search by length, price, ammenities, and more.

With YachtLife, chartering a luxury yacht has never been easier or more affordable.

YACHTLIFE FEATURES:

• Split the cost of your yacht charter among any number of guests.
• Share your code with friends and both earn $250 credit off your yacht charter.
• Easily compare prices and specifications of multiple luxury yachts at once.
• Favorite yachts to see later in your favorite section.
• Share a yacht with your friends via social media or SMS.
• Charter a luxury yacht with credit card, or bank account (multi-day charters only).

MEMBERSHIP PROGRAM:

We’ve taken the luxury yacht charter experience to the next level and launched The YachtLife Membership Club. The club is designed for companies and individuals that would like to entertain family, friends, and business associates on yachts throughout the year.

MEMBERSHIP BENEFITS:

• One personalized membership.
• Members-only pricing on all yacht charters (savings of 10-20%).
• Dedicated YachtLife concierge to assist with bookings and special requests.
• Exclusive discounts and offers on products and services offered by our suite of luxury
brand and hospitality partners.
• VIP access to YachtLife and partner events throughout the year.

YACHTLIFE LOCATIONS:

US + Canada + Mexico:
• Florida (Miami, Fort Lauderdale, Naples, Palm Beach, Key West)
• California (Newport Beach, Marina Del Rey, San Diego)
• Mexico (Los Cabos, Vallarta, Cancun)

• Vancouver, British Colombia (Canada)
• Chicago, IL
• Washington D.C.
• Newport, RI

Once you create your YachtLife profile, you’ll be able to browse our entire global yacht charter fleet. You can always ask a question or call for further information on any yacht. Reserve a luxury yacht for your desired date, duration, pickup time, and the number of guests. Our yacht charter specialists will receive your request and confirm your yacht charter.

YachtLife operates in 30+ markets worldwide with over 500 private yachts available for yacht charter. Search by length, price, ammenities, and more.

With YachtLife, chartering a luxury yacht has never been easier or more affordable.

YACHTLIFE FEATURES:

• Split the cost of your yacht charter among any number of guests.
• Share your code with friends and both earn $250 credit off your yacht charter.
• Easily compare prices and specifications of multiple luxury yachts at once.
• Favorite yachts to see later in your favorite section.
• Share a yacht with your friends via social media or SMS.
• Charter a luxury yacht with credit card, or bank account (multi-day charters only).

MEMBERSHIP PROGRAM:

We’ve taken the luxury yacht charter experience to the next level and launched The YachtLife Membership Club. The club is designed for companies and individuals that would like to entertain family, friends, and business associates on yachts throughout the year.

MEMBERSHIP BENEFITS:

• One personalized membership.
• Members-only pricing on all yacht charters (savings of 10-20%).
• Dedicated YachtLife concierge to assist with bookings and special requests.
• Exclusive discounts and offers on products and services offered by our suite of luxury
brand and hospitality partners.
• VIP access to YachtLife and partner events throughout the year.
